Text: Could it be that you're not a ghost at allâ€”

As is the glory of my family, and my pride as a
knight of Velgalta. With everything lost to me, I
fell like a shooting star, and vanished forevermore.

Must've put you in a panic, her suddenly starting to
catch on like that.

Annerose may well have known from the beginning
that I wasn't dead.
I'm not so sure of that.

Although I'm sure...she wanted Lady Karen to be
alive.

Because that's how I might've felt if I were her,
that's all.

...Let's go check on Lady Zeta. She said she's fine
on her own, but anything could happen.

(Annerose Nichtsehen. A pure, honest knight, the
likes of which are all too rare these days.)

(It brings me heartfelt joy to have been able to
entrust my hopes as Karen von Herzog to you.)
What... Why is she such an empty shell?!

This is insane! Intentionally using these Templar
goons like human shields!

Someone who came to help her friends in need
wouldn't fight so carelessly as that...!

Wh-What...?! What is this awful, sickly sweet
stench?

If you aren't going to stop preaching that stupid
garbage...
A fight to the death really is all we have left!

You called me your friend! But in the end, this is
how it was destined to be, Saint!
What...? There's something wrong with her!

And that nasty smell just nowâ€”something's
happening to her!
